          <p>If the above method returns true the puzzlesForBoardSet() function (defined above) is called with the vector as an argument and the result is added to the puzzles array.</p>
          <div><pre className="line-numbers"><code className="language-typescript">puzzles.push(puzzlesForBoardSet(vector));</code></pre></div>
